data.description: This 5 BR home includes an office, guest room with bath, game-room/loft, extended patio and other beautiful functional features that have made this Castlerock (Silverthorne) a favorite.  The  16 ft wall of windows, and beautiful stairwell along joining wall creates a bright open space. Solar Panels installed in 2019! Interior has been freshly painted and is clean. No need to build, this one is move-in ready.  Currently not occupied, so the home STAYS clean. Realtor lives in the 'hood & sanitizes after showings. Located in award winning community - Santa Rita Ranch.  Only 30 minutes to Killeen, TX and Ft Hood and 15 minutes to Austin Metro Light Rail in Leander, 20-25 minutes to Georgetown, Round Rock, Cedar Park.  Liberty Hill Schools - Text Agent - GO.
